{"type":"text","timestamp":1778981529564,"sessionID":"ses_1cc731d29ffeAv83jd6twnaLta","part":{"id":"prt_e338fd43d001GqB0ojTfvgnLHv","messageID":"msg_e338fcd54001ETsvN5GmMw9mOO","sessionID":"ses_1cc731d29ffeAv83jd6twnaLta","type":"text","text":"Implemented the fix for issue `#3651` and committed it locally.\n\nWhat changed:\n- Removed the two serialized GO ghost frames from `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`.\n- Added equivalent OWL `DisjointClasses` axioms to `src/ontology/components/disjoint_union_over.owl`:\n  - `GO:0005623` disjoint with `UBERON:0000001`\n  - `GO:0110165` disjoint with `UBERON:0000001`\n\nWhy:\n- This preserves the intended disjointness semantics while avoiding the OBO serializer behavior that creates unlabeled GO term frames in the edit file.\n\nValidation:\n- Re-serialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert -i src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo -f obo -o src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`\n- Reviewed the diff to confirm only the intended changes were made\n\nCommit:\n- `0c7ae76` `Move GO disjoints to OWL component`\n\nCreated and left uncommitted:\n- `ISSUE_COMMENTS.md`\n- `PR_COMMENTS.md`\n\nNotes:\n- I committed only the ontology files I edited.\n- The workspace has unrelated pre-existing changes and untracked evaluation files, which I left untouched.\n","time":{"start":1778981524541,"end":1778981529561}}}
